{"tid":2500804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東方衞視傳禁出鏡  滬查6主播赴周正毅壽宴","createTime":"2021-04-23T02:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T02:28:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10e92454798d60be1baa74dacf9d32d084cf9999","tid":2500804,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210422/RIA37BQFNNEULP6YR4BRJ7B3WE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210422%2FRIA37BQFNNEULP6YR4BRJ7B3WE%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrWWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=737426b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210422%2FRIA37BQFNNEULP6YR4BRJ7B3WE%2F&h=bc89e7fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210422/RIA37BQFNNEULP6YR4BRJ7B3WE/</a><br />\n<br />\n東方衞視傳禁出鏡 <br />\n滬查6主播赴周正毅壽宴<br />\n<br />\n【貶損形象】去年出獄的上海前首富周正毅，日前筵開多席慶祝60歲生日，六名當紅的上海東方衞視主持人到場致辭賀壽，詎料這觸動到上海當局的神經。上海廣播電視18日發聲明指「加強對主持人參與社會公眾活動的管理，確保不再參與與個人身份和形像不符的社會活動。」據傳，上述人等及當晚的主持人已被禁出鏡，有人甚至被列入黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：涉貪囚近20年 廉署仍通緝<br />\n<br />\n周正毅本月18日於上海外灘萬達瑞華酒店舉行壽宴，同晚還舉行微商品牌「花界」的發佈活動。舞台正中央置有「不忘初心 回歸本色」及「周正毅先生生日晚宴」字樣，出席者板上簽名，猶如影視盛會。多名男女在台上集體亮相，逐一發言，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KyqBg2oXF_iufkff6njZY1IZBTI=/510x349/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DVPXRVKRBVF6NH5ZYSA24MVZQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKyqBg2oXF_iufkff6njZY1IZBTI%3D%2F510x349%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDVPXRVKRBVF6NH5ZYSA24MVZQM.jpg&h=afd0c33e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周正毅出獄後辦六十大壽，東方衞視主持人陳蓉到賀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ytYue9QPR2OQSRhQAjRUl1buXe4=/510x270/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/27YHLHBRAVBSBKWVSLKXVPD3ZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FytYue9QPR2OQSRhQAjRUl1buXe4%3D%2F510x270%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F27YHLHBRAVBSBKWVSLKXVPD3ZE.jpg&h=a68e7041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■六名當紅上海東方衞視主持人到場致辭賀壽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用「公子」稱呼周<br />\n<br />\n東方衞視六名知名主持人，陳蓉、倪琳、戴劉菲、房海燕、程雷和朱楨亦有到場賀壽，逐個對周正毅「祝福」。台上女主持笑言今次東方衞視「傾巢出動」，該台的春晚「也只不過是這個陣容」。東方衞視當家花旦陳蓉在台上表示：「我是剛剛認識周公子，雖然是周公子的新朋友，但。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n程雷更是「世界仔」上身，稱在上海灘不認識周正毅是說不過去的，他自己知道周正毅20多年，但上個月才認識他，也。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/piwTrZE5UlTaL6pjuBbW5PDUOzw=/510x559/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3YUAYCOPLVGKNJDKLQ2LES2ROY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpiwTrZE5UlTaL6pjuBbW5PDUOzw%3D%2F510x559%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3YUAYCOPLVGKNJDKLQ2LES2ROY.jpg&h=db4333e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■宴會極其隆重，佈景有「不忘初心回歸本色」八字。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n非壽宴主持 否認收出場費<br />\n<br />\n有知情人士公開了上海廣播電視台（東方衞視的上級機構）的聲明。聲明指出，六名主持人均指受邀出席壽宴，非為壽宴擔當主持，同時否認收取「出場費」。聲明最後指出：「上海廣播電視台將進一步調查事件，並要求各頻道盡快約談涉事主持人&hellip;&hellip;同時切實加強對主持人參與社會公眾活動的管理，確保不再參與與個人身份和形象不符的社會活動。」<br />\n<br />\n隨後再有知情人士發佈了一張微信截圖，陳蓉、倪琳、海燕、程雷和朱楨不准出鏡；。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這張截圖未能確定真假，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據內地企業調查網站「企查查」顯示，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n微博/《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8xbx7pYW0WxInoZ9vsWGfWqMG1g=/510x730/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UKWDKAUF2RAJ5K45WR7EQSVXM4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8xbx7pYW0WxInoZ9vsWGfWqMG1g%3D%2F510x730%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUKWDKAUF2RAJ5K45WR7EQSVXM4.gif&h=7c212af5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}